{"tid":1501205,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"朦朧詩人楊煉獻給香港人的一首詩:","createTime":"2019-08-24T09:51:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T09:51:08.000Z","uid":267381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"70dde779ff44d2c8e21873e9333e04850f4eae73","tid":1501205,"uid":267381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T09:51:08.000Z","msg":"你們是星，我們是夜；<br />\n你們點燃，我們熄滅；<br />\n你們是漢，我們是奸；<br />\n你們淚熱，我們心死；<br />\n你們赴死，我們偷生；<br />\n你們走上街頭，我們縮進沙發；<br />\n你們為明天而流血，我們為今天而苟活；<br />\n你們珍視愛的寶貴，我們死守命的價錢；<br />\n你們三十年前還沒出生，我們三十年後已經腐爛&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/749695385/posts/10162036342870386?s=517538694&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F749695385%2Fposts%2F10162036342870386%3Fs%3D517538694%26sfns%3Dmo&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOhVTfDkzAunSCULMKrq9Td0%3D&h=a808a012\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/749695385/posts/10162036342870386?s=517538694&amp;sfns=mo</a>"}]}